<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc2141b7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2386"><num value="2386">§ 2386.</num><heading> Transfer of installations without charge</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The transfer of any municipal installation authorized to be made under the provisions of this subchapter may be made without charge to the entity receiving the installation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc2141b8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-04/ch543">Aug. 4, 1955, ch. 543</ref>, ch. 8, § 86, <ref href="/us/stat/69/481">69 Stat. 481</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
